HEADWORD: Amphi-
<hw>Am*phi-</hw>. <ety>[Gr. <grk>'amfi`</grk>.]</ety> <def>A prefix in
words of Greek origin, signifying <xex>both</xex>, <xex>of both
kinds</xex>, <xex>on both sides</xex>, <xex>about</xex>,
<xex>around</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
